{"tid":1635894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日一齊去送學生番學！","createTime":"2019-10-07T15:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:14:13.000Z","uid":331758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b978de30f7d3f337aaddf49a892415f25cd97a","tid":1635894,"uid":331758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:37:15.000Z","msg":"教育局要求中學提交戴口罩人數 學生斥營造白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=a8c7bc27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a> 新聞<br />\n<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=a8c7bc27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a> 新聞2019年10月7日 上午8:30 [UTC]<br />\n【Now新聞台】教育局要求全港中學周二提交戴口罩學生人數，有中學生形容是白色恐怖。中學校長會主席鄧振強相信，局方是希望掌握學生的情緒，教育局指每日都與學校聯絡，但不會蒐集個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n教育局周末前向全港學校發信，提醒學生禁蒙面法的內容，又指除宗教或健康原因，校內外都不應戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n教育局要求全港中學在新例實施後首個上學日上午11時前，向分區主任提交戴口罩、罷課，或參與校外人鏈活動的人數。<br />\n<br />\n有中學生認為教育局是向校方及同學施壓，強調會繼續堅持表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n教育局發言人回應指，由新學年開始，教育局每日都與學校聯絡，了解學校情況，包括學生提出罷課的情況，及其他特殊事件，強調從來沒有亦不會蒐集個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣係唔會令我地驚嫁<br />\n係白色恐怖面前 <br />\n我知大家都會驚會唔會俾人秋後算帳<br />\n但好多學生都冒住呢個危險係到發聲<br />\n我地應該要去支持佢地"},{"pid":"a6854c46d6e57a538b62ef5cff34bc9007adfeb2","tid":1635894,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"借個位黎用吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全港最黃嘅光時網物平台於10月7日上線啦!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629141</a>"},{"pid":"df0c2ed68fa74aa4c1c8fbfd358d1d23a8a3618c","tid":1635894,"uid":130035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b68c1e4c4bf75ba0c16dfc7bc0ce4fe405815e","tid":1635894,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"點秋後算帳<br />\n踢出校?"},{"pid":"428e1749c9ac2440aba041a2f468f90b3666cda1","tid":1635894,"uid":331758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89b68c1e4c4bf75ba0c16dfc7bc0ce4fe405815e","tid":1635894,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"點秋後算帳<br />\n踢出校?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:14:13.000Z","msg":"唔知佢地會做咩<br />\n但係都要鼓勵下班學生既士氣<br />\n俾佢地知唔係只係得佢地一個人"}]}